        <section>
            <p><indexterm>hardware requirements for VMware</indexterm>The external disk space varies
                depending on the number of logs planned to be stored, as shown in the table
                below.</p>
            <table frame="all" rowsep="1" colsep="1" id="table_al2_5gz_c5b">
                <title>No. of Logs versus Disk Space</title>
                <tgroup cols="2">
                    <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                    <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*"/>
                    <thead>
                        <row>
